  <brief_title>Subchondral Microfracture of Tibia After Arthroscopic Anterior Cruciate Ligament Surgery Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Subchondral Microfracture of Tibia After Arthroscopic Anterior Cruciate Ligament Surgery Reconstruction With Two Different Drilling Techniques. Correlation With Postoperative Pain</official_title>
  <sponsors>
